#: src/qualcoder/information.py:454
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Manage\n"
"\n"
"The Manage tab displays workspaces for organising cases, files, attributes, "
"journals, and references.\n"
"Use the [Manage menu](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases) to choose among "
"them.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Files](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_files)\n"
"\n"
"- This menu lets you add and remove empirical data in your project.\n"
"- You can import plain text and many other document types,\n"
"including PDFs, images, audio, and video.\n"
"- You may also import survey data.\n"
"- Before importing text files, you may want to create pseudonyms to protect "
"the privacy of people or organisations.\n"
"- [Help: Import files](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Files/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Cases](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_cases)\n"
"\n"
"- You can use cases to group files together that are related to a topic, "
"person, organisation, or any other empirical entity in your study. \n"
"- This can be useful for organising your data and for running reports on "
"specific groups of files.\n"
"- [Help: Cases](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Journals](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Journals are used to record your thoughts when coding and analysing "
"data. \n"
"- The journal window opens separately from the main window so you can move "
"between them easily.\n"
"- [Help: Journals](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage Attributes](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Files, cases, and journals can have attributes (variables) that describe "
"their characteristics. \n"
"- They can be used to filter and organise data, and to run reports based on "
"specific criteria. \n"
"- Use this menu to create and manage such attributes. They can be attached "
"to files, cases, and journals directly in the respective workspaces. \n"
"- [Help: Attributes](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Manage References](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_references)\n"
"\n"
"- Bibliographic references can be imported from NBIB and RIS files.\n"
"- After that, references can be linked to files in the project.\n"
"- [Help: Import References](qualcoder://help/6.1.-Imports-and-Exports/)\n"
msgstr ""
"# Jere\n"
"\n"
"Tab Jere a afiche espas travay pou òganize ka, dosye, atribi, jounal, ak "
"referans.\n"
"Sèvi ak [menu Jere a](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases) pou chwazi pami yo.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jere Fichye](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_files)\n"
"\n"
"- Meni sa a pèmèt ou ajoute ak retire done anpirik nan pwojè w la.\n"
"- Ou ka enpòte tèks senp ak anpil lòt kalite dokiman,\n"
"tankou PDF, imaj, odyo, ak videyo.\n"
"- Ou ka enpòte done sondaj tou.\n"
"- Anvan ou enpòte fichye tèks, ou ka vle kreye pseidonim pou pwoteje vi "
"prive moun oswa òganizasyon.\n"
"- [Ede: Enpòte fichye](qualcoder://help/3.2.-Files/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jere Ka yo](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_cases)\n"
"\n"
"- Ou ka itilize ka yo pou gwoupe fichye ki gen rapò ak yon sijè, yon moun, "
"yon òganizasyon, oswa nenpòt lòt antite empirik nan etid ou a. \n"
"- Sa ka itil pou òganize done ou yo epi pou fè rapò sou gwoup fichye "
"espesifik.\n"
"- [Ede: Ka](qualcoder://help/3.3.-Cases/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jere Jounal](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_journals)\n"
"\n"
"- Ou itilize jounal yo pou anrejistre panse w pandan w ap kode ak analize "
"done yo. \n"
"- Fenèt jounal la louvri apa de fenèt prensipal la pou w ka deplase ant yo "
"fasilman.\n"
"- [Èd: Jounal](qualcoder://help/5.2.-Journals/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jere Atribi](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_attributes)\n"
"\n"
"- Fichye, ka, ak jounal ka genyen atribi (varyab) ki dekri karakteristik "
"yo. \n"
"- Yo ka itilize pou filtre ak òganize done, epi pou kouri rapò ki baze sou "
"kritè espesifik. \n"
"- Sèvi ak meni sa a pou kreye ak jere atribi sa yo. Yo ka atache ak fichye, "
"ka, ak jounal dirèkteman nan espas travay respektif yo. \n"
"- [Èd: Atribit](qualcoder://help/3.4.-Attributes/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Jere Referans](qualcoder://menu/files_and_cases/manage_references)\n"
"\n"
"- Ou ka enpòte referans bibliyografik apati de fichye NBIB ak RIS.\n"
"- Apre sa, ou ka lye referans yo ak fichye ki nan pwojè a.\n"
"- [Ede: Enpòte Referans](qualcoder://help/6.1.-Imports-and-Exports/)"

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:503
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Coding\n"
"\n"
"The Coding tab displays workspaces for coding text, PDFs, images, audio, and "
"video.\n"
"Use the [Coding menu](qualcoder://menu/coding) to select an option to "
"begin. \n"
"Note that you can only open a particular coding workspace if that type of "
"data is actually present in the current project. \n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Text](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to read textual data closely and assign codes to "
"selected passages.\n"
"- You can organise codes in a tree, add memos and annotations, create "
"bookmarks, and mark especially useful segments as important.\n"
"- [Help: Coding text](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Images](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_image)\n"
"\n"
"- In this workspace, you can select regions in photographs, diagrams, "
"screenshots, or other visual material and assign codes to them.\n"
"- Coded areas are displayed as coloured rectangles linked to your code "
"system.\n"
"- [Help: Coding images](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Audio and Video](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_audio_video)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to transcribe and/or code time-based media such as "
"interviews, focus groups, and field recordings.\n"
"- [Help: Coding audio and video](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-and-"
"Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code PDFs](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- This workspace allows you to code text directly in PDF documents when you "
"want to keep the original page layout in view.\n"
"- This is useful for articles, reports, and other source material where page "
"position and formatting matter.\n"
"- [Help: Coding PDFs](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Assisted Coding](qualcoder://menu/coding/ai_assisted_coding)\n"
"\n"
"- This loads a variant of the text coding workspace that uses AI to explore "
"your data and suggest segments for a selected code.\n"
"- [Help: AI assisted coding](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Code Organiser](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Use this workspace to reorganise your code system using a graphical, mind-"
"map style interface.\n"
"- You can move, merge, and rename codes and categories as your analytic "
"structure becomes clearer.\n"
"- [Help: Code Organiser](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Colour Scheme](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour_scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- This allows you to change the colour scheme of your codes and "
"categories. \n"
"- Special schemes for colour-blind users are available. \n"
msgstr ""
"# Kodaj\n"
"\n"
"Tab Kodaj la afiche espas travay pou kode tèks, PDF, imaj, odyo, ak videyo.\n"
"Itilize [Meni Kodaj la](qualcoder://menu/coding) pou chwazi yon opsyon pou "
"kòmanse. \n"
"Remake ke ou ka louvri yon espas travay kodaj patikilye sèlman si kalite "
"done sa a aktyèlman prezan nan pwojè aktyèl la.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kode Tèks](qualcoder://menu/coding/codes)\n"
"\n"
"- Sèvi ak espas travay sa a pou li done tèksyèl yo ak anpil atansyon epi "
"asiyen kòd pou pasaj ki seleksyone yo.\n"
"- Ou ka òganize kòd yo nan yon pyebwa, ajoute memo ak anotasyon, kreye makè, "
"epi make segman ki espesyalman itil kòm enpòtan.\n"
"- [Èd: Kode tèks](qualcoder://help/4.1.-Coding-Text/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kode Imaj](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_image)\n"
"\n"
"- Nan espas travay sa a, ou ka chwazi zòn nan foto, dyagram, kapti ekran, "
"oswa lòt materyèl vizyèl epi ba yo kòd.\n"
"- Zòn ki kode yo parèt kòm rektang kolore ki lye ak sistèm kòd ou a.\n"
"- [Èd: Kode imaj](qualcoder://help/4.4.-Coding-Images/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kode Odyo ak Videyo](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_audio_video)\n"
"\n"
"- Sèvi ak espas travay sa a pou transkri ak/oswa kode medya ki baze sou tan "
"tankou entèvyou, gwoup diskisyon, ak anrejistreman sou teren.\n"
"- [Èd: Kode odyo ak videyo](qualcoder://help/4.5.-Coding-Audio-and-Video/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kode PDF](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_pdf)\n"
"\n"
"- Espas travay sa a pèmèt ou kode tèks dirèkteman nan dokiman PDF lè ou vle "
"kenbe fòma paj orijinal la vizib.\n"
"- Sa itil pou atik, rapò, ak lòt materyèl sous kote pozisyon paj ak fòma yo "
"enpòtan.\n"
"- [Ede: Kode PDF yo](qualcoder://help/4.3.-Coding-Text-on-PDFs/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Kodaj Asiste pa Entèlijans Atifisyèl](qualcoder://menu/coding/"
"ai_assisted_coding)\n"
"\n"
"- Sa a chaje yon varyant espas travay kodaj tèks la ki itilize Entèlijans "
"Atifisyèl (AI) pou eksplore done w yo epi sijere segman pou yon kòd ki "
"seleksyone.\n"
"- [Ede: Kodaj ak asistans AI](qualcoder://help/4.2.-AI-Assisted-Coding/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Òganizatè Kòd](qualcoder://menu/coding/code_organiser)\n"
"\n"
"- Sèvi ak espas travay sa a pou reòganize sistèm kòd ou a avèk yon entèfas "
"grafik ki gen stil kat lespri.\n"
"- Ou ka deplase, fizyone, epi chanje non kòd ak kategori yo pandan estrikti "
"analiz ou a ap vin pi klè.\n"
"- [Èd: Òganizatè Kòd](qualcoder://help/4.6-Code-Organiser/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Eskèm Koulè](qualcoder://menu/coding/colour_scheme)\n"
"\n"
"- Sa pèmèt ou chanje palèt koulè kòd ou yo ak kategori ou yo. \n"
"- Gen palèt espesyal ki disponib pou moun ki gen pwoblèm pou wè koulè."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:560
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# Reports tab\n"
"\n"
"This tab displays tools from both the [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis) "
"and [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports) menus.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analysis](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want to explore coded segments and relationships in "
"detail.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Retrieval and segment-based analysis\n"
"\n"
"These tools help you inspect the actual coded material in your project.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code retrieval](qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding_reports) is a flexible "
"analysis tool. It gathers all segments for selected codes or categories and "
"lets you narrow the results by file, case, attributes, or search text.\n"
"- [Codes by text segments](qualcoder://menu/analysis/text_segments_by_codes) "
"generates a table with text segments and all associated codes.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Code relationships and overlaps\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools to examine how codes relate to one another. They only work "
"with text files.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code relations](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_relations) shows "
"proximity, overlap, inclusion, and exact matches between selected codes.\n"
"- [Code co-occurrence](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_co_occurrence) focuses "
"on where two codes overlap or directly touch.\n"
"- [Code text exact matches](qualcoder://menu/analysis/"
"code_text_exact_matches) lists passages where different codes were applied "
"to exactly the same text.\n"
"- [Graph](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view_graph) provides a visual, mind-map "
"style view of linked project elements like codes, cases, files, etc. [Help: "
"Graph](qualcoder://help/5.4.-Graph/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Reports](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Use these tools when you want summaries, comparisons, counts, charts, or "
"exports for reporting purposes.\n"
"\n"
"[Help: Analysis and Reports menu options](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Inter-Coder Comparisons\n"
"\n"
"- [Coding comparison](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison) and "
"[Coding comparison by file](qualcoder://menu/reports/"
"coding_comparison_by_file) are especially useful for collaborative work and "
"inter-coder checking.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Summaries, frequencies, and charts\n"
"\n"
"These reports summarise patterns across the project rather than showing "
"every coded segment in detail.\n"
"\n"
"- [Code frequencies](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_frequencies) counts how "
"often codes and categories have been used.\n"
"- [Code counts by file/case](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_comparison_table) "
"gives a compact overview of where selected codes appear most often.\n"
"- [File summary](qualcoder://menu/reports/file_summary) and [Code summary]"
"(qualcoder://menu/reports/code_summary) give focused overviews of one file "
"or one code at a time.\n"
"- [Charts](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) visualises distributions and "
"comparisons with diagrams such as bar charts, treemaps, and heatmaps.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Advanced reporting\n"
"\n"
"- [Database queries](qualcoder://menu/reports/sql_statements) gives direct "
"access to the project database for custom analyses. This is most useful when "
"the standard reports do not answer a specific research question in the exact "
"form you need.\n"
msgstr ""
"# Tab Rapò yo\n"
"\n"
"Tab sa a afiche zouti ki soti nan meni [Analiz](qualcoder://menu/analysis) "
"ak [Rapò](qualcoder://menu/reports) yo.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analiz](qualcoder://menu/analysis)\n"
"\n"
"Sèvi ak zouti sa yo lè ou vle eksplore segman ki kode yo ak relasyon yo an "
"detay.\n"
"\n"
"[Ede: Opsyon meni Analiz ak Rapò](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Rekiperasyon ak analiz ki baze sou segman\n"
"\n"
"Zouti sa yo ede w enspekte materyèl ki kode aktyèl la nan pwojè w la.\n"
"\n"
"- [Rekiperasyon Kòd](qualcoder://menu/analysis/coding_reports) se yon zouti "
"analiz ki fleksib. Li rasanble tout segman pou kòd oswa kategori ki "
"seleksyone yo epi li pèmèt ou sere rezilta yo pa fichye, ka, atribi, oswa "
"tèks rechèch.\n"
"- [Kòd pa segman tèks](qualcoder://menu/analysis/text_segments_by_codes) "
"jenere yon tablo ki gen segman tèks yo ak tout kòd ki asosye avèk yo.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Relasyon ant kòd yo ak sipèpozisyon\n"
"\n"
"Sèvi ak zouti sa yo pou egzamine kijan kòd yo gen rapò youn ak lòt. Yo "
"fonksyone sèlman ak fichye tèks.\n"
"\n"
"- [Relasyon kòd yo](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_relations) montre "
"pwoksimite, sipèpozisyon, enklizyon, ak korespondans egzak ant kòd ki "
"seleksyone yo.\n"
"- [Ko-okirans kòd](qualcoder://menu/analysis/code_co_occurrence) konsantre "
"sou kote de kòd sipèpoze oswa manyen youn lòt dirèkteman.\n"
"- [Match egzak tèks kòd yo](qualcoder://menu/analysis/"
"code_text_exact_matches) bay yon lis pasaj kote diferan kòd te aplike sou "
"egzakteman menm tèks la.\n"
"- [Graf](qualcoder://menu/analysis/view_graph) bay yon vi vizyèl, nan stil "
"kat lespri, sou eleman pwojè ki konekte yo tankou kòd, ka, fichye, elatriye. "
"[Èd: Graf](qualcoder://help/5.4.-Graph/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Rapò](qualcoder://menu/reports)\n"
"\n"
"Sèvi ak zouti sa yo lè ou vle rezime, konparezon, kantite, graf, oswa "
"ekspòtasyon pou rezon rapò.\n"
"\n"
"[Ede: Opsyon meni Analiz ak Rapò](qualcoder://help/5.3.-Reports/)\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Konparezon Ant Kòdè\n"
"\n"
"- [Konparezon kodaj](qualcoder://menu/reports/coding_comparison) ak "
"[Konparezon kodaj pa fichye](qualcoder://menu/reports/"
"coding_comparison_by_file) itil anpil pou travay an kolaborasyon ak pou "
"verifikasyon ant kodè yo.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Rezime, frekans, ak graf\n"
"\n"
"Rapò sa yo rezime modèl yo atravè pwojè a olye pou yo montre chak segman ki "
"kode an detay.\n"
"\n"
"- [Frekans kòd yo](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_frequencies) konte konbyen "
"fwa yo itilize kòd ak kategori yo.\n"
"- [Kantite kòd pa fichye/ka](qualcoder://menu/reports/code_comparison_table) "
"bay yon apèsi tou kout sou ki kote kòd chwazi yo parèt pi souvan.\n"
"- [Rezime fichye](qualcoder://menu/reports/file_summary) ak [Rezime kòd]"
"(qualcoder://menu/reports/code_summary) bay yon apèsi detaye sou yon sèl "
"fichye oswa yon sèl kòd alafwa.\n"
"- [Graf](qualcoder://menu/reports/charts) vizyalize distribisyon ak "
"konparezon avèk dyagram tankou graf a ba, treemaps, ak kat chalè.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Rapò avanse\n"
"\n"
"- [Kwè baz done](qualcoder://menu/reports/sql_statements) bay aksè dirèk nan "
"baz done pwojè a pou analiz pèsonalize. Sa itil anpil lè rapò estanda yo pa "
"reponn yon kesyon rechèch espesifik nan fòm egzak ou bezwen an."

#: src/qualcoder/information.py:621
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"# AI Agent\n"
"\n"
"Here, you can interact with the [AI Agent](qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-"
"based-analysis/) to\n"
"explore your empirical text data, get suggestions for coding, obtain "
"feedback on your codes or memos,\n"
"and generate summaries and reports. To begin, use the [\"New\" button]"
"(qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new) at \n"
"the bottom left and choose one of the options described below.\n"
"\n"
"{{AI_WARNING_BLOCK}}\n"
"\n"
"## [Chat with the AI Agent](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_general_chat)\n"
"\n"
"- This is the default starting point for an open-ended analysis or any other "
"task.\n"
"- You can also ask for help using QualCoder.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Topic Exploration](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/"
"new_topic_exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Search and explore a topic or question across the whole corpus of project "
"data.\n"
"- This option opens a dialog where you define the topic and select which "
"data to include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Text Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_text_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Analyse a selected text passage from your empirical material in detail.\n"
"- This will switch to the text coding workspace and let you select a passage "
"for analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [AI Code Analysis](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_code_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Discuss your codings with the AI Agent, compare different codes, generate "
"subcodes, or create reports.\n"
"- This will also open a dialog to select the code(s) and data you want to "
"include in the analysis.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Other Options\n"
"- The [AI permissions](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/permissions) control at the "
"bottom left lets you choose what \n"
"the AI Agent is allowed to do in your project.\n"
"- Open the [AI menu](qualcoder://menu/ai) for more options, for example to "
"edit predefined prompts in the\n"
"[prompt library](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_prompts), or start [AI assisted "
"coding](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_search_and_coding).\n"
msgstr ""
"# Ajan IA\n"
"\n"
"Isit la, ou ka kominike ak [Ajan IA a](qualcoder://help/5.1.-AI-chat-based-"
"analysis/) pou\n"
"eksplore done tèks anpirik ou yo, jwenn sijesyon pou kodaj, jwenn fidbak sou "
"kòd ou yo oswa memo ou yo,\n"
"epi jenere rezime ak rapò. Pou kòmanse, itilize [bouton \"Nouvo\" a]"
"(qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new) ki anba agoch la epi chwazi youn nan opsyon "
"ki dekri anba yo.\n"
"\n"
"{{AI_WARNING_BLOCK}}\n"
"\n"
"## [Chat ak Ajan AI a](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_general_chat)\n"
"\n"
"- Sa a se pwen depa pa defo pou yon analiz ouvè oswa nenpòt lòt travay.\n"
"- Ou ka mande èd tou sou fason pou itilize QualCoder.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Eksplorasyon Sijè ak AI](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/"
"new_topic_exploration)\n"
"\n"
"- Chèche epi eksplore yon sijè oswa yon kesyon nan tout korpus done pwojè "
"a.\n"
"- Opsyon sa a ouvri yon bwat dyalòg kote w ap defini sijè a epi chwazi ki "
"done pou enkli nan analiz la.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analiz Tèks AI](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_text_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Analize an detay yon pasaj tèks ou chwazi nan materyèl anpirik ou a.\n"
"- Sa ap chanje w pou ale nan espas travay kodaj tèks la epi l ap pèmèt ou "
"chwazi yon pasaj pou analiz.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## [Analiz Kòd AI](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/new/new_code_analysis)\n"
"\n"
"- Diskite sou kodaj ou yo ak Ajan IA a, konpare diferan kòd, jenere soukòd, "
"oswa kreye rapò.\n"
"- Sa ap louvri yon bwat dyalòg tou pou w chwazi kòd(yo) ak done ou vle mete "
"nan analiz la.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"## Lòt Opsyon\n"
"- Kontwòl [Pèmisyon AI](qualcoder://ai_agent_tab/permissions) ki anba agoch "
"la pèmèt ou chwazi sa \n"
"Ajàn AI a gen dwa fè nan pwojè ou a.\n"
"- Louvri [men AI a](qualcoder://menu/ai) pou plis opsyon, pa egzanp pou "
"modifye kòmand predefini yo nan\n"
"[bibliyotèk prompt](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_prompts), oswa kòmanse [kodaj ak "
"asistans AI](qualcoder://menu/ai/ai_search_and_coding)."

